# Embedded libraries — load FIRST. LibSharedMedia surfaces textures/fonts other
# addons register (e.g. StoneTweaks' custom textures) into our picker; needs
# LibStub + CallbackHandler first. LibCustomGlow provides the aura glow effects
# (Autocast/Pixel/Proc/Action-Button) and needs LibStub.
Libs\LibStub\LibStub.lua
